{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServerSignalName\/newConnection"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServerSignalName"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Emitted when a new authenticated connection has been made. Use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_dbus_connection_get_peer_credentials()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to figure out what","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"identity (if any), was authenticated."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusserversignalname\/newconnection"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO20DBusServerSignalNameO13newConnectionyA2CmF","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"newConnection"}],"symbolKind":"case","title":"DBusServerSignalName.newConnection","roleHeading":"Case","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"newConnection","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you want to accept the connection, take a reference to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"connection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object and return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":". When you are done with the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connection call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dbus_connection_close()"},{"text":" and give up your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"reference. Note that the other peer may disconnect at any time -"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a typical thing to do when accepting a connection is to listen to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the [DBusConnection](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusconnection\/onclosed(flags:handler:) signal."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServer"},{"type":"text","text":" contains "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"runInThread"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then the signal is emitted in a new thread dedicated to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connection. Otherwise the signal is emitted in the thread-default","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"main context (see [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.MainContext.push_thread_default"},{"text":"])","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the thread that "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"server"},{"type":"text","text":" was constructed in."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You are guaranteed that signal handlers for this signal runs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"before incoming messages on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"connection"},{"text":" are processed. This means","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that it’s suitable to call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dbus_connection_register_object()"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"similar from the signal handler.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusServer":{"title":"DBusServer","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusserver","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusServer"},{"type":"text","text":" is a helper for listening to and accepting D-Bus"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connections. This can be used to create a new D-Bus server, allowing two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"peers to use the D-Bus protocol for their own specialized communication."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A server instance provided in this way will not perform message routing or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"implement the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/dbus.freedesktop.org\/doc\/dbus-specification.html#message-bus-messages","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusServer","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServer","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusServer"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusServerSignalName/newConnection":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServerSignalName\/newConnection","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"newConnection"}],"title":"DBusServerSignalName.newConnection","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Emitted when a new authenticated connection has been made. Use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_dbus_connection_get_peer_credentials()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to figure out what","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"identity (if any), was authenticated.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusserversignalname\/newconnection"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusServerSignalName":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusServerSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusserversignalname","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/d